      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n* Update oven-sh/setup-bun action to v2 by @renovate[bot] in https://github.com/ckt1031/obsidian-tinypng-plugin/pull/55\r\n* Small fixes + #57 by @DlfnAntx in https://github.com/ckt1031/obsidian-tinypng-plugin/pull/58\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @DlfnAntx made their first contribution in https://github.com/ckt1031/obsidian-tinypng-plugin/pull/58\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/ckt1031/obsidian-tinypng-plugin/compare/0.3.0...0.4.0",
